* [[Pentagon Memorial]], [[The Pentagon]], [[Arlington County, Virginia]]
* [[Tribute in Light]], World Trade Center site (temporary/periodic)
* [[9/11 Memorial (Arizona)|9/11 Memorial]], [[Wesley Bolin Memorial Plaza]], [[Phoenix, Arizona]]
* [[Tear of Grief]]
* ''[[Postcards (memorial)|Postcards]]'', [[Staten Island, New York]]
* Memorial, [[Eisenhower Park]], [[East Meadow, New York]]
* [[The Rising (9/11 memorial)|The Rising]], [[Kensico Dam]] Plaza, [[Valhalla, New York]]
* [[Empty Sky (memorial)|Empty Sky]], [[Liberty State Park]], New Jersey
* Garden of Reflection, [[Yardley, Pennsylvania]]
* Beverly Hills 9/11 Memorial Garden, [[Beverly Hills, California]]<ref>[http://beverlyhills911memorial.com/ "Beverly Hills 9/11 Memorial Garden"]. Retrieved May 28, 2012.</ref>
* Seaford 9/11 Memorial, [[Seaford, New York]]<ref>[http://seaford911.org/ "Seaford 9/11 Memorial"]. Retrieved May 28, 2012.</ref>
* Freedom Plaza, [[Metuchen, New Jersey]]
